highlights.text: “Only You Freestyle” by Headie One and Drake is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 77 spots at #74.
Juice WRLD has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Come & Go (with Marshmello)” is the highest at #12.
“cardigan” by Taylor Swift is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #1.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 186 weeks straight.
